1111
01:24:29.982 --> 01:24:32.860
I'm Spike. and this
is me mum. Isla.

1112
01:24:32.943 --> 01:24:34.695
Spike. Isla.

1113
01:24:34.778 --> 01:24:36.862
And this is a baby.

1114
01:24:38.991 --> 01:24:40.367
