1115
01:24:42.202 --> 01:24:43.245
Come on. then.

1116
01:24:43.328 --> 01:24:45.497
We need to go
before he wakes up.

1117
01:24:54.881 --> 01:24:56.174
What's that?

1118
01:24:59.553 --> 01:25:00.679
I've been...

1119
01:25:01.680 --> 01:25:03.974
I've been waiting almost

1120
