Keep going. that's good.

1152
01:29:18.144 --> 01:29:19.145
Good lad.

1153
01:29:21.273 --> 01:29:22.940
Alas. poor Erik.

1154
01:29:28.154 --> 01:29:29.781
Choose a place for him.

1155
01:29:55.015 --> 01:29:58.643
Very nice. Well done. Spike.

1156
