1189
01:32:15.321 --> 01:32:19.117
Either way. it has metastasized.

1190
01:32:20.869 --> 01:32:24.289
It explains your symptoms.
and. I'm afraid...

1191
01:32:24.372 --> 01:32:27.834
the masses on your
breasts and lymph nodes.

1192
01:32:31.129 --> 01:32:33.631
