1218
01:34:05.515 --> 01:34:06.933
If you tell us where
one was I can...

1219
01:34:07.016 --> 01:34:08.643
-I can go. and I can get it.
-Spike. Spike. Listen to me.

1220
01:34:08.726 --> 01:34:09.853
