1246
01:36:19.941 --> 01:36:23.653
Remember we must die.

1247
01:36:23.736 --> 01:36:25.154
And it's true.

1248
01:36:26.197 --> 01:36:28.074
There are many kinds of death...

1249
01:36:30.952 --> 01:36:32.996
