1295
01:46:09.154 --> 01:46:11.031
No!

1296
01:46:11.365 --> 01:46:13.199
Spike!

1297
01:46:19.123 --> 01:46:21.458
Spike!

1298
01:47:21.769 --> 01:47:22.811
Fuck.

1299
01:47:32.821 --> 01:47:34.031
Oh!

